{"tid":1491314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：暫時不需要全港停課　相信警方不會隨便進入學校執法","createTime":"2019-08-20T11:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:35:43.000Z","uid":212626,"like":53,"dislike":476,"uniUserReply":138,"replies":[{"pid":"c6ef5c7c31a5dc56d2d75700f9532a737d81edd1","tid":1491314,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"反《逃犯條例》修訂風波不斷，有學生組織發起9月2日開學日起罷課行動。教育局局長楊潤雄就支援學校迎接新學年進行準備工作舉行記者會，表示教育局今日已向全港中小學發表一份「作好準備迎接新學年」附錄，<span style=\"color: red;\">強調堅決反對任何形式的罷課</span>，不論罷課1日或每周罷課1日，都會影響學生學業、情緒及師生間的關係。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄表示，任何人士都不應利用學校作為表達政治訴求的場地，亦不應以學生的參與作為施壓的手段，影響他們正常學習，並相信教師會以教育學生為首要職責，而討論社會時事亦屬正常，重申罷課不是解決問題方法，應該多溝通尋找解決方法才是正確途徑，若以罷課成了爭取個別訴求的手段，日後肯定不斷出現。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄又指，是否需要停課需視乎個別情況，<span style=\"color: red;\">但暫時看不到有全港性停課的需要</span>。他表示相信警方不會隨便進入學校執法，認為現行機制已足夠處理。他又指近月示威衝突可能影響學生及教師情緒，教師應保持中立客觀，以不同角度分析事件，學校亦應保持緊密溝通，舉辦活動讓學生表達情緒，訓練學生多角度思考，增強抗逆力。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e6%9a%ab%e6%99%82%e7%9c%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%88%b0%e9%9c%80%e5%85%a8%e6%b8%af%e6%80%a7%e5%81%9c%e8%aa%b2-%e6%a5%8a%e6%bd%a4%e9%9b%84%ef%bc%9a%e5%8f%8d%e5%b0%8d%e4%bb%bb%e4%bd%95%e5%bd%a2%e5%bc%8f%e7%bd%b7%e8%aa%b2-185493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e6%259a%25ab%25e6%2599%2582%25e7%259c%258b%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%2588%25b0%25e9%259c%2580%25e5%2585%25a8%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%2580%25a7%25e5%2581%259c%25e8%25aa%25b2-%25e6%25a5%258a%25e6%25bd%25a4%25e9%259b%2584%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%258f%258d%25e5%25b0%258d%25e4%25bb%25bb%25e4%25bd%2595%25e5%25bd%25a2%25e5%25bc%258f%25e7%25bd%25b7%25e8%25aa%25b2-185493&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9v1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=7a05a0c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e6%9a%ab%e6%99%82%e7%9c%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%88%b0%e9%9c%80%e5%85%a8%e6%b8%af%e6%80%a7%e5%81%9c%e8%aa%b2-%e6%a5%8a%e6%bd%a4%e9%9b%84%ef%bc%9a%e5%8f%8d%e5%b0%8d%e4%bb%bb%e4%bd%95%e5%bd%a2%e5%bc%8f%e7%bd%b7%e8%aa%b2-185493</a>"},{"pid":"ec879abdbff6066888769947ac32dc8de20dd376","tid":1491314,"uid":55597,"like":244,"dislike":1,"score":243,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:31:41.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄都冇權指揮警察，憑咩信佢"},{"pid":"b15857ab73e03e0e7fdfe07f201f8666e91889b3","tid":1491314,"uid":219530,"like":224,"dislike":1,"score":223,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"咁大反應<br />\n做對了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da14a3894ebf40826877eaca26d5e04315d7aea4","tid":1491314,"uid":7168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b15857ab73e03e0e7fdfe07f201f8666e91889b3","tid":1491314,"uid":219530,"like":224,"dislike":1,"score":223,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"咁大反應<br />\n做對了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372f33e09ff159594930d5d68f4e4778c78f0f33","tid":1491314,"uid":92448,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:35:36.000Z","msg":"相信警方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天大笑話"},{"pid":"c8dae403b1facb9a58fe862809f0bd3dc8c73cf7","tid":1491314,"uid":34612,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:36:00.000Z","msg":"我地要connect 埋00 後10 後"},{"pid":"92f046b26afefade631dba9bc5e495880d807df3","tid":1491314,"uid":8880,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:36:27.000Z","msg":"堅決反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家d狗官用埋d大陸tone"},{"pid":"d8f8a1dcbae26004ec11ebba418bac94f966a19b","tid":1491314,"uid":194298,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:36:59.000Z","msg":"需唔需要係你決定架？<br />\n看得自由於那麼高"},{"pid":"897c3c25fd8ee25f293515d1