es/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1922329123b600417ad3ae5a77ccd759038c3bfa","tid":1491314,"uid":293804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:55:32.000Z","msg":"罷課要你批准<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d045e9e5dd8203c3ca496284fadb205840c155ae","tid":1491314,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:56:17.000Z","msg":"梗係唔會入喇<br />\nd 老師 學生 係學校跳樓 都唔會報警既<br />\n打消防咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae474f6868000a53d08d11632f0a811b28f40f32","tid":1491314,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6ef5c7c31a5dc56d2d75700f9532a737d81edd1","tid":1491314,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"反《逃犯條例》修訂風波不斷，有學生組織發起9月2日開學日起罷課行動。教育局局長楊潤雄就支援學校迎接新學年進行準備工作舉行記者會，表示教育局今日已向全港中小學發表一份「作好準備迎接新學年」附錄，<span style=\"color: red;\">強調堅決反對任何形式的罷課</span>，不論罷課1日或每周罷課1日，都會影響學生學業、情緒及師生間的關係。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄表示，任何人士都不應利用學校作為表達政治訴求的場地，亦不應以學生的參與作為施壓的手段，影響他們正常學習，並相信教師會以教育學生為首要職責，而討論社會時事亦屬正常，重申罷課不是解決問題方法，應該多溝通尋找解決方法才是正確途徑，若以罷課成了爭取個別訴求的手段，日後肯定不斷出現。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄又指，是否需要停課需視乎個別情況，<span style=\"color: red;\">但暫時看不到有全港性停課的需要</span>。他表示相信警方不會隨便進入學校執法，認為現行機制已足夠處理。他又指近月示威衝突可能影響學生及教師情緒，教師應保持中立客觀，以不同角度分析事件，學校亦應保持緊密溝通，舉辦活動讓學生表達情緒，訓練學生多角度思考，增強抗逆力。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e6%9a%ab%e6%99%82%e7%9c%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%88%b0%e9%9c%80%e5%85%a8%e6%b8%af%e6%80%a7%e5%81%9c%e8%aa%b2-%e6%a5%8a%e6%bd%a4%e9%9b%84%ef%bc%9a%e5%8f%8d%e5%b0%8d%e4%bb%bb%e4%bd%95%e5%bd%a2%e5%bc%8f%e7%bd%b7%e8%aa%b2-185493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e6%259a%25ab%25e6%2599%2582%25e7%259c%258b%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%2588%25b0%25e9%259c%2580%25e5%2585%25a8%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%2580%25a7%25e5%2581%259c%25e8%25aa%25b2-%25e6%25a5%258a%25e6%25bd%25a4%25e9%259b%2584%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%258f%258d%25e5%25b0%258d%25e4%25bb%25bb%25e4%25bd%2595%25e5%25bd%25a2%25e5%25bc%258f%25e7%25bd%25b7%25e8%25aa%25b2-185493&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9v1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=7a05a0c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e6%9a%ab%e6%99%82%e7%9c%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%88%b0%e9%9c%80%e5%85%a8%e6%b8%af%e6%80%a7%e5%81%9c%e8%aa%b2-%e6%a5%8a%e6%bd%a4%e9%9b%84%ef%bc%9a%e5%8f%8d%e5%b0%8d%e4%bb%bb%e4%bd%95%e5%bd%a2%e5%bc%8f%e7%bd%b7%e8%aa%b2-185493</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:57:21.000Z","msg":"罷唔罷課<br />\n關佢撚事"},{"pid":"39c35ac652edf0235f76a97fa5822fe45a673a1d","tid":1491314,"uid":290647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"罷課都關黑警事 ？黑警而家咁有責任心既咩？"},{"pid":"d3d34b277853474259b3f6df55a4e44af5e84710","tid":1491314,"uid":282902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"完全無想像過班狗會入中學捉人，無端端咁講，即係班毒官有人提過咁做！"},{"pid":"2c4ea44e3719a0bead883596dc2e409c130f338c","tid":1491314,"uid":160162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:05:24.000Z","msg":"支持罷課"},{"pid":"8d96806b33895c4a769932e2b465aab4ebb03e8d","tid":1491314,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"真係以為自已話到事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933ab08ebdb5ff732151c819dbdb3845fb67f03e","tid":1491314,"uid":185022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"你覺得冇需要啫<br />\n我地覺得有喎<br />\n<br />\n我地夠話唔要普教中啦～<br />\n又唔撚見你聽<br />\nonL9"},{"pid":"f40b405a76f7abf2f802498ddd78a2adaa37692b","tid":1491314,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63ed6ec43201785a215e6fe3